Package org.blockchainnative.metadata

Class EventInfo<TEventFieldInfo extends EventFieldInfo,TEventParameterInfo extends EventParameterInfo>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.blockchainnative.metadata.EventInfo<TEventFieldInfo,TEventParameterInfo>
  • Type Parameters:
    TEventFieldInfo - Concrete type of the EventFieldInfo objects used by EventInfo.
    TEventParameterInfo - Concrete type of the EventParameterInfo objects used by EventInfo.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EthereumEventInfo, FabricEventInfo
    public class EventInfo<TEventFieldInfo extends EventFieldInfo,TEventParameterInfo extends EventParameterInfo>
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds additional information about a smart contract event.

    It is recommended to use ContractInfoBuilder and its subtypes to construct instances of this class.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    ContractInfoBuilder, ContractInfo, ContractWrapperGenerator
